casebody.data:
No. 642,

Misc.

Irvin v. Indiana. Petitioner pro se. Edwin K. Steers, Attorney General of Indiana, and Owen S. Boling and Richard M. Givan, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondent.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Indiana denied without prejudice to filing for federal habeas corpus after exhausting state remedies.
